<br>
Let me state this though:<br>
<br>
1). You have over 30 level 60's now, and at least 5 60 wariors in full HOT+Dozekar gear.<br>
<br>
2). All of your key classes have epics+ weapons.<br>
<br>
3). Over half of your core players have spent a month or more on legends buying every droppable item they can, up to and including NToV drops and rights to no drop items. (With RL cash in many cases). It's a well known fact on Stormhammer now that SZ neuts are just there to gear up cheaply.<br>
<br>
