<br>
5). So, after 10 months of a server whining we are &quot;bloobie poons&quot; and how it's unfair we have better gear, etc ... you finally zerg down a simple mob we've been killing for months, and run to brag on <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>every</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--> message board imaginable. (This is at least the third board I've seen something like this on in the last 15 minutes already).<br>
<br>
